1.0.0.name: wordpress/pdalex-glossary
1.0.0.description:
This plugin creates a glossary for your WordPress powered site. It will create an additional section in the admin panel, where you can add new terms to your glossary

A few notes about the sections above:

  • "Browse glossary" here you will see all terms.
  • "Add term" here you will add new term.
